        <abstract> 
<p>CD should not be discouraged by the bulk of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>. CD’s suggestion to print technical details in small type is good.</p> 
            <p>Murray has sent MS to a "man of letters and good information" as an experiment to test its effect. Has no intention of throwing up publication.</p>
